<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Online Bookstore</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .company-overview {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .news-updates {
      background-color: #f8e3bb;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Include Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Online Bookstore</a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/about">About Us</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
          <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/categories">Book Categories</a></li>
         
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
  

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <header class="py-5 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Learn more about our story, our mission, and the latest updates.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
      <!-- Company Overview Section (First Section) -->
      <div class="col-12">
        <div class="company-overview">
          <h3 style="text-align: center;">Company Overview</h3> <br>
          <p>Welcome to our online bookstore. We are passionate about providing the best selection of books for readers of all kinds. Whether you're looking for the latest bestsellers, classic literature, or niche genres, we have something for everyone.</p>
          <p>Founded in [Year], we have grown to become a trusted destination for book lovers, offering convenient online shopping and fast delivery services. Our goal is to make reading accessible and enjoyable for all, and we are constantly updating our inventory to reflect the latest trends in the literary world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- News and Updates Section (Second Section) -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
      <div class="col-12">
        <div class="news-updates">
          <h3 style="text-align: center;">News and Updates</h3> <br>
          <p><strong>New Book Launch: "The Great Adventure"</strong></p>
          <p>We're excited to announce the release of our latest title, "The Great Adventure", a thrilling novel by author John Doe. Available now in hardcover, paperback, and e-book formats.</p>

          <p><strong>Special Discount: 20% Off Your First Order!</strong></p>
          <p>Sign up for our newsletter and enjoy 20% off your first order. Don't miss out on this limited-time offer!</p>

          <p><strong>Upcoming Events</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Author Meet & Greet: </strong>Join us on [Date] for a special event with author Jane Smith, where she'll be discussing her latest book and answering questions from fans.</li>
            <li><strong>Book Signing Event: </strong>On [Date], we will host a book signing with author Bob Brown at our flagship store. Get your copy signed and meet the author in person!</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Include Footer -->
  <%- include('footer') %>

  <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
